    <p class="gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Prepare your local authority children’s services for Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Directors of local authority children’s services in England need to prepare, so they can minimise disruption to their services if there’s a no-deal Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

